WEBVTT

1
00:33:26.320 --> 00:33:27.590 
撞折了我的小手指
Broke my pinkie.

2
00:33:27.610 --> 00:33:29.460 
- 什么 - 他看起来不壮
- What? - He didn't look that big,

3
00:33:29.490 --> 00:33:31.210 
但他的手臂像砖墙那样结实
but his arm was like a brick wall.

4
00:33:31.300 --> 00:33:33.590 
- 是啊 他的手臂很结实 - 太丢人了
- Yeah, he had strong arms. - It was humiliating.

5
00:33:33.610 --> 00:33:35.370 
隔天上班我不得不编故事
The next day at work I had to make up a story

6
00:33:35.390 --> 00:33:37.990 
- 说我在公园遭抢劫了 - 你没告诉过我这些
- about being mugged in the park. - You never told me any of this.

7
00:33:38.190 --> 00:33:40.190 
这还不算是我最
Well... it wasn't my most...

8
00:33:40.260 --> 00:33:42.390 
男子气概的轶事
manly anecdote.

9
00:33:45.460 --> 00:33:48.630 
我真的恨他伤了你心 唉
I sure hate that he hurt you, boy.

10
00:33:50.040 --> 00:33:51.720 
谢了
Thanks.

11
00:33:51.950 --> 00:33:54.000 
下次记得找个
Make sure the next guy you get involved with

12
00:33:54.020 --> 00:33:55.480 
上身力量很弱的男人
has very weak upper body strength.

13
00:33:55.510 --> 00:33:57.270 
- 一定会 - 我想为你出头
- Of course. - I'd like to defend your honor.

